headline: Zoetis Declares Third Quarter 2025 Dividend
summary: PARSIPPANY, N.J., May 21, 2025--The Board of Directors of Zoetis Inc. (NYSE:ZTS) has declared a dividend of $0.50 per share for the third quarter of 2025. The dividend will be paid on Wednesday, September 3, 2025, to all holders of record of the Company’s common stock as of the close of business on Friday, July 18, 2025.
